last_episode_to_air.overview: A surprise diagnosis from Dr. Santos worries Loren as she and Alexei try to throw Asher's first birthday party. As the due date grows closer, Loren starts to develop contractions a little too soon, causing panic that they might have another NICU baby.

overview: Follows couples from 90 Day Fiance after the 90 days are over.

episodes.name: David & Annie: Plus Two
episodes.overview: Five years ago, David and Annie tied the knot and created a happy life for themselves in the US. Now, they're returning to Annie's village in Thailand to bring home her brother and cousin and give them an opportunity for an education in America.

episodes.name: Loren & Alexei: Two Under 2
episodes.overview: Loren and Alex have their hands full raising their 1-year-old baby, Shai, and now they are getting ready to bring on baby number two. As if raising two under 2 wasn't stressful enough, Loren learns that Alex is going to Israel without her.

episodes.name: David & Annie: Gobble Gobble
episodes.overview: Trying to convince the elders in Annie's family that they'll be good guardians isn't going too well for David and Annie, so David tries to win them over by taking them on a family trip and finally making good on his overdue dowry.

episodes.name: Loren & Alexei: Look Who's Walking
episodes.overview: Alex returns home to Israel for the first time in two years, leaving behind a pregnant Loren. As Alex happily reunites with family and friends for a cousin's wedding, Loren struggles with loneliness and taking care of their newly walking toddler.

episodes.name: David & Annie: The Runaway
episodes.overview: David and Annie decide it's time to travel to the root of Aunt Lom's disapproval. Then, when Jordan runs away at a critical moment, Annie worries that he might not even want to go to America.

episodes.name: Loren & Alexei: Mommy And Me
episodes.overview: On his last day in Israel, Alex reveals his plan to bring his parents to America, and Loren's parents may not like it. Meanwhile, Loren meets up with a friend from her pre-baby life and tries to make new friends at a local "Mommy and Me" class.

episodes.name: David & Annie: Change Of Plans
episodes.overview: With everyone's blessings, David, Annie, Amber and Jordan leave the village and head to Bangkok for the kids' visa interviews; the family hits another roadblock.

episodes.name: Loren & Alexei: False Alarm
episodes.overview: While Alex takes Shai for swimming lessons, Loren receives some alarming news from the doctor; to keep her mind at ease, Loren spends the day shopping with her mom and planning a mini babymoon with Alex

episodes.name: David & Annie: The Big Day
episodes.overview: As lockdown rules ease, David and Annie take the kids fishing to relieve their cabin fever. Once they are finally able to schedule visa interviews, worry starts to creep in that Jordan may not be as prepared as Amber.

episodes.name: Loren & Alexei: Let The Babymoon Begin
episodes.overview: With the news that the baby may arrive sooner than expected, Loren and Alex shift gears and decide to go on a local babymoon. Also, the couple still needs to figure out the best way to tell Loren's parents about their plan to move out-of-state.

episodes.name: David & Annie: Supernatural Setbacks
episodes.overview: David and Annie dread breaking the news to the family about the kids' failed visa interviews. When suspicions arise that their bad luck is the work of bad spirits surrounding David, he and Annie seek the advice of a local spirit communicator.

episodes.name: Loren & Alexei: The Future Is Now
episodes.overview: Loren seeks advice from her psychic while her parents complain to their other daughter about Loren and Alex's potential move out of state. Loren uses all her tricks to get a reluctant Alex to interview doula candidates with her.

episodes.name: David & Annie: The Lost Boy
episodes.overview: After a visit with the local witch doctor reveals that a protective spirit has been obstructing their efforts, David and Annie's plan to calm the spirit with another blessing ceremony is derailed when Jordan goes missing.

episodes.name: Loren & Alexei: It's Go Time
episodes.overview: Alex keeps Loren laughing through her tears as she is rushed in for an emergency C-section. Arriving almost a month early, Baby Boten is immediately placed into the NICU instead of her parents' arms, leaving Loren and Alex anxious and sad.

episodes.name: David & Annie: The Year Of The Tiger
episodes.overview: With time running out for the kids to get visas before the school year starts in the US, David and Annie struggle with Jordan's behavior and hope to avoid the choice of leaving Jordan behind or risking Amber's last chance.

episodes.name: Loren & Alexei: All Of Loren's Boys
episodes.overview: Loren and Alex are put to the test as days turn into weeks in the NICU for baby Boten. When they finally get the word that he's strong enough to go home, the couple scrambles to prepare for his arrival.

1.name: Season 1
1.overview: David & Annie - Season 1 / Loren & Alexei - Season 1

episodes.name: David & Annie: Better Luck This Time
episodes.overview: After multiple failed attempts to get her brother and cousin a visa to come to the US, David and Annie finally head back to Thailand to try again. This time, they plan on bringing two of David's family members with them.

episodes.name: Loren & Alexei: Table For Five
episodes.overview: Hardly managing two kids under 2, Loren and Alex discover that another baby is on the way. As they contemplate their future, the couple entertain the idea of moving to Israel, but breaking the news to Loren's parents will prove to be difficult.

episodes.name: David & Annie: Let The Trip Begin
episodes.overview: David and Annie finally make their way back to Thailand with his daughter and granddaughter along for the adventure. After returning to the village, everyone welcomes them with open arms -- except for Jordan, who still carries a grudge against Annie.

episodes.name: Loren & Alexei: Birthday Bashed
episodes.overview: Alex attempts to get Shai involved in sports while Loren fumbles at trying to get him into modeling. Loren and Alex throw a birthday bash for Shai, but things aren't all fun and games when Marlene decides to carry on about the potential Israel move.

episodes.name: David & Annie: Chicken Nightmares
episodes.overview: Annie continues to get Ashley and Aubri more accustomed to life in her village by showing them how to prepare a Thai feast. At dinner, David reveals his plans for this trip, but Aunt Lom's negativity puts a damper on things once again.

episodes.name: Loren & Alexei: Pins And Needles
episodes.overview: Overwhelmed from planning for a family vacation to Israel, Loren decides to visit an acupuncturist for stress relief. Meanwhile, Alex is challenged to take the boys out for a day of fun, but he finds out that juggling the two of them isn't so easy.

episodes.name: David & Annie: Happy Buddha
episodes.overview: After Ashley and Aubri head back to America, David and Annie return to the village to prepare for David's upcoming monk ceremony. Aunt Lom adds fuel to the fire by informing them of some shocking news.

episodes.name: Loren & Alexei: A Big Surprise
episodes.overview: A family picnic in Israel gets dramatic when Loren and Alexei's plan to move to Israel is mentioned. As the couple enjoys a day at the beach with old friends, Bryan and Marlene continue to voice their disapproval of the move to Alexei's parents.

episodes.name: David & Annie: David The Monk
episodes.overview: As David learns the rules and regulations of being a monk, Annie finally has a long-overdue heart-to-heart with Jordan. After getting through his first day in monkhood, David is forced to deal with all of the elements that night brings

episodes.name: Loren & Alexei: I Know Her Better
episodes.overview: As the family trip in Israel continues, Bryan and Marlene grow increasingly frustrated with Loren and Alexei's constant talk of moving, leading Bryan to confront Alexei about potential legal ramifications if they decide to go through with it.

episodes.name: David & Annie: Temple Toilet Cleaner
episodes.overview: David must deal with grueling physical tasks to complete his three days of monkhood while barely being able to sleep through the night. Meanwhile, Annie prepares Amber to get into the habit of speaking English, and Cindy gives Aunt Lom a makeover.

episodes.name: Loren & Alexei: Shut Up
episodes.overview: Bryan and Marlene join Loren and Alexei on a trip to a Kibbutz as the family tries to put their differences behind them. A fiery blowout erupts between mother and daughter after a tension-filled family day.

episodes.name: David & Annie: The Best Sperm
episodes.overview: After arriving in Phuket, David wastes no time getting everyone to try out American cuisine for the first time. While Jordan and Amber get enrolled in language school to study for their visa interview, David and Annie head to an OBGYN.

episodes.name: Loren & Alexei: the Last Supper
episodes.overview: Bryan and Marlene decide to skip out on a farewell meal with Alexei's parents, which further drives a wedge between them. As Loren continues to process the heated argument with her mom, she feels that moving to Israel might be best for everyone.

episodes.name: David & Annie: One Step Forward, One Step Back
episodes.overview: While Annie and the girls have a fun day at the pool, David and Jordan share a heart-to-heart at a Muay Thai boxing gym. Jordan's secrets throw a wrench in David and Annie's plans once again.

episodes.name: Loren & Alexei: From Bad To Worse
episodes.overview: As the rift with her family continues, Loren tries her best to manage tasks without any help from them. When her parents and sister all refuse to babysit, however, Loren wonders if their broken bonds will ever be put back together.

episodes.name: David & Annie: Rollercoaster Rookies
episodes.overview: To ease the pressure of school, David and Annie take Jordan and Amber to an amusement park for a fun-filled day. Worried that Jordan will back out of his upcoming interview, David asks Cindy to speak with him in hopes of changing his mind.

episodes.name: Loren & Alexei: RSVP
episodes.overview: To take her mind off of family tension, Alexei brings Loren and the boys to a local waterpark for a fun-filled day. Later, he surprises her with a birthday dinner, but unexpected news about her upcoming baby shower nearly ruins it.

episodes.name: David & Annie: Just The Beginning
episodes.overview: David and Annie do practice runs with Amber and Jordan to get them prepared for their looming visa interviews, but Jordan's lack of enthusiasm has them nervous. When the family receives unexpected news, David tries to find another possible solution.

episodes.name: Loren & Alexei: Last Second Surprise
episodes.overview: Loren takes Asher to his first modeling photoshoot while Bryan gives Marlene and Rebecca an ultimatum about the family tension. Loren enjoys her friends' company at her baby shower, but a surprise guest appearance leaves her shocked and speechless.

episodes.name: Loren & Alexei: Birth Special!
episodes.overview: A surprise diagnosis from Dr. Santos worries Loren as she and Alexei try to throw Asher's first birthday party. As the due date grows closer, Loren starts to develop contractions a little too soon, causing panic that they might have another NICU baby.
